Class Rayd

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.joml.Rayd
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable

    public class Rayd
extends Object
implements Externalizable
    Represents a ray with a given origin and direction using double-precision floating-point numbers.
    Author:
    Kai Burjack
    See Also:
